# Code and Syntax Highlighting

Markdown supports code blocks and syntax highlighting.

## Inline Code

Use backticks to highlight inline code, like `console.log('Hello, world!');`.

## JavaScript Example

```javascript
function greet(name) {
    return `Hello, ${name}!`;
}
console.log(greet('World'));
```

